text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It combines
information on voting rights, the freedom and fairness of elections, freedoms of association and expression, as
well as the extent to which citizens can engage in regional and local government, civil society organizations, and
direct democracy. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); HYDE (2017); Gapminder (2022); UN (2022)
